Ahhh sus voces...LOS OT6 cantando en un escenario esta canción, la voz de MJ no tiene igual, su control sobre las notas altas, es sencilamente un talento sin igual. La voz de Eunwoo profunda y acariciando en la parte que habla.
Además con performance como éstas, demuestran que su talento no es solo baile y sincronía, que son un grupo completo.
Ayyyy , solo quiero ver a los OT6 sobre un escenario cantando todas las canciondes de BF Y GATEWAY . Espero sea luego.
Fighting ASTRO,

snippet.textDisplay:
For the past 12 days Astro has been my world. Some wld say that's  sad. It was sadder before. I do in fact have 'a weak heart'  and you all have an idea of what it's like with covind19.  
But Astro generously shares their life of that special brand of music   Kpop  their love  and laughter and yes, sorrow and so I have lived, tho vicariously, a colourful lite in a drab place.  Restrictions will end and the intensity will most likely not be the same next cb. 
 The whips "Get str3aming", "faster" "we can".  No-one would dare say that to me in real life. But I warmed up my working hand, my 2nd hand clunky laptop said hello to having only naps (just happened, no alarms) and enjoyed it all even forgiving YT. 
Obviously they didn't appreciate all our effort but they don't tell us exactly why tho there are lots of don'ts. I've been reading them and I know not all my effort counted at the start. The sticky point being MAYBE there's  a finite no. to 1 IPaddress an hour. I consoled myself with an e,g, someone related that when BTS released ON their 24 hour count of 83?M was reduced to 48M. YT tells it from the point of view of an uploader wanting to receive $$$. 
It was, like KNOCK, an unforgettable experience. By cb8 computer fixed, apps downloaded  method worked out. Recommend reading YT docs yourself.
Got all that off my chest. Congrats if u got here. You're tenacious, just the sort to stream for 12 days  Hope real congrats will be given to the babies later today. So glad they have each other close by.

It was, like KNOCK, an unforgettable experience. By cb8 computer fixed, apps downloaded  method worked out. Recommend reading YT docs yourself.
